# Generated run artifacts are NOT committed — each harness run writes a new
# timestamped report/log here. One example set (the 20260617T182214Z-* trio,
# the --mock format reference) is tracked deliberately; everything else is
# ignored so real runs never clutter the tree.
*
!.gitignore
!20260617T182214Z-report.json
!20260617T182214Z-report.txt
!20260617T182214Z.log
